bilingual.source: The governor granted a commutation of his sentence.
The governor issued a reprieve for the death row inmate.
bilingual.target: 州长为死刑犯发布了缓刑。

bilingual.source: The governor commuted the prisoner's life sentence.
bilingual.target: 州长将囚犯的无期徒刑减刑了。

bilingual.source: The incumbent governor is running for re-election next year.
bilingual.target: 现任的州长明年将竞选连任。

bilingual.source: The governor announced he is pardoning several prisoners.
bilingual.target: 州长宣布他正在赦免几名囚犯。

bilingual.source: The governor announced new policies to improve education.
bilingual.target: 州长宣布了改善教育的新政策。

bilingual.source: The governor of the prefecture announced new policies today.
bilingual.target: 行政区的州长今天宣布了新政策。

bilingual.source: The governor addressed the legislature about the budget crisis.
bilingual.target: 州长向立法机关就预算危机发表了讲话。

bilingual.source: The governor signed the bill into law after much debate.
bilingual.target: 经过多次辩论，州长签署了该法案使其成为法律。

list.abstract: governor，英语单词，主要用作名词，作名词时意为“主管人员、统治者、管理者、[自] 调节器、地方长官”。

yingyinNormal.en: I spoke at length last night with Governor Conway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我昨晚跟康威州长深谈过。

yingyinNormal.en: Anything to put a Democrat into the governor's mansion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能让民主党人进入州长府邸就好。

yingyinNormal.en: What? Your wife, Mr. Governor. Eli, I said no.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？你妻子，州长先生。伊莱，我说不行。

yingyinNormal.en: Any illegality? Any illegality. By the governor?
yingyinNormal.zh: 任何非法行为? 任何的非法行为。州长的非法行为?

yingyinNormal.en: Right. If you testify against Governor Florrick, you risk disbarment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 明白了，如果你出庭指证了福瑞克州长，就有被取消律师资格的风险。

yingyinNormal.en: You wanted to include the Governor, I want to include Ahmadi.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想叫上州长，我想叫上艾哈迈德。

yingyinNormal.en: Jim, do you have a problem with my wife? No, no, Mr. Governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 吉姆，你跟我妻子有过节吗？不，没有，州长先生。

yingyinNormal.en: But, the District of Columbia. No governor. Just you, the mayor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，哥伦比亚特区，没有州长，只有你，一个市长。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, he's a terrorist sympathizer, and you're the wife of the governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，但他支持恐怖主义，而且你是州长夫人。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, the one lawyer, Florrick, her husband's about to be governor of Illinois.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有个律师，福瑞克，她老公要当伊利诺伊州长了。

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks for dropping by, Jim. Thanks for your time. Eli. Jim. Governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你过来，吉姆。谢谢你的时间，伊莱。吉姆，州长。

yingyinNormal.en: I got a lot of champs, chiefs, sports. I even got a governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很多人叫我“冠军”“领袖”“体育委员”，还有人叫我“州长”。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that was the shortest honeymoon period in history. One month as a governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这算是史上最短的新官蜜月期了做了一个月的州长

yingyinNormal.en: Is this sudden change of plans a result of your meeting with Governor Conway yesterday?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这次突然计划变动是您昨天与康威州长会晤导致的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: There is one idea we could try. Eli, could you step in here a minute? Mr. Governor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有个办法我们可以试试，伊莱，能过来一下吗？州长先生。

yingyinNormal.en: The governor has put the execution on hold, Eddie. They don't want to try a third time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 州长已经暂停执行死刑了，艾迪，他们不想再试第三次了 。

yingyinNormal.en: Alicia, don't try to sell me. You are the governor's wife. Your name means something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾丽西娅，别把我卖了，你是州长夫人，你的名字意味着些什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it wouldn't surprise me if ICO accelerated their plans, because of the governor's comments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果州长的言论促使哈里发国加速计划，我也不会惊奇。

yingyinNormal.en: Senate? Possibly. Or governor, 2020. And the president's on board with this? Completely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 参议员吗？或许，或者州长，2020年。总统也同意吗？完全同意。

yingyinNormal.en: The relationship between two lawyers on Governor Florrick's legal team bears a direct relationship to. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 福瑞克州长的法律团队中，两名律师的关系直接影响到。不。

examination_example.sentence: California's plan, which is expected to be finalized by the <highlight>governor</highlight> next year, should serve as a model.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 加州的计划预计将在明年由州长敲定，应该可以作为一个模范。

examination_example.sentence: In Wisconsin the unions have rallied thousands of supporters against Scott Walker, the hardline Republican <highlight>governor</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在威斯康星州，工会召集了数千名支持者反对强硬的共和党州长斯科特·沃克。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.zh: 州长; 总督; 主管; 理事; 董事

examination_example.sentence: He felt surprised, angry, dirty and disappointed, and finally decided to give up running for <highlight>Governor</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他感到惊讶、愤怒、肮脏且失望，最后决定放弃竞选州长。

examination_example.sentence: Mr. Mark Twain, a candidate for <highlight>Governor</highlight>, was convicted of perjury by thirty-four people, in Wakawak, in 1863.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1863年，州长候选人马克·吐温先生在瓦卡越被34人判定为伪证罪。

examination_example.sentence: Why did Mr. Twain finally decide to give up running for <highlight>Governor</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么吐温先生最终决定放弃竞选州长？
